nodes.text: 100 and Counting is an article written by Pablo Hidalgo and published in January 2013's Star Wars Insider 139. It looks back at the history of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars animated series and lists every episode aired in production order. 100 and Counting Expanded, a follow-up to this article, later appeared in Star Wars Insider 150.
The article was reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2018.
